filters.name: BarbBlock
filters.description: BarbBlock is a content blocking list with standalone browser extensions for Chrome and Firefox. It blacklists sites which have used DMCA takedowns to force removal from other content blocking lists. Such takedowns are categorically invalid, but they can be effective at intimidating small open-source projects into compliance.

filters.name: Fanboy's Cookiemonster List

filters.name: NoCoin Filter List
filters.description: This filter disables browser based miners such as coin-hive.

filters.name: Dandelion Sprout's Nordic Filters

For more information, details, helpful tools, and other lists that I've made, visit https://github.com/DandelionSprout/adfilt/blob/master/Wiki/General-info.md#english.

filters.name: Filter unblocking search ads and self-promotion
filters.description: Filter that unblocks search (Duckduckgo, Google, Bing, Yahoo) and self-promo ads. Self-promotion definition: when an ad on a website is promoting this very website or other websites/social media/etc closely related to it, such ad is considered a self-promoting one.

filters.name: AdvBlocker Mobile Ads filter

filters.name: AdvBlocker Safari filter
